{"tid":2294215,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"重慶民營企業家李懷慶煽顛等罪成　判囚20年凍結全數資產","createTime":"2020-11-21T00:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T09:02:51.000Z","uid":53062,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"462396d2273ef7758b602053d00dc8d337d9d5a0","tid":2294215,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T00:19:37.000Z","msg":"重慶市第一中級法院裁定他全部罪名成立，判處有期徒刑20年，剝奪政治權利3年，名下資產全數凍結。李懷慶8名員工也被判處徒刑，刑期4年從16年不等。<br />\n<br />\n54歲的李懷慶是重慶市人，被捕前為重慶富華典當公司的老闆；他長期關注和資助弱勢社群及救助塵肺病患者，2018年初他與妻兒及一批公司員工被重慶警方拘捕，被指控加入名為「環球實報」的微信群組造謠，轉發批評政權的文章，並轉發提及「暴力革命」的錄音。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20201120/s00004/1605876959620/%E9%87%8D%E6%85%B6%E6%B0%91%E7%87%9F%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%AE%B6%E6%9D%8E%E6%87%B7%E6%85%B6%E7%85%BD%E9%A1%9B%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A20%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E5%85%A8%E6%95%B8%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20201120%2Fs00004%2F1605876959620%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2585%25B6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2587%259F%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2587%25B7%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%2585%25BD%25E9%25A1%259B%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A20%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%2594%25A2&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3%2B4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=ace867d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20201120%2Fs00004%2F1605876959620%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2585%25B6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2587%259F%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2587%25B7%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%2585%25BD%25E9%25A1%259B%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A20%2